long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Displays NCVER nationally agreed nominal hours for a unit of competency on https://training.gov.au/. 

Based on the nationally agreed nominal hours from NCVER:
https://www.ncver.edu.au/rto-hub/statistical-standard-software/nationally-agreed-nominal-hours

This plugin is using the following version of the dataset:
Nationally agreed nominal hours By NCVER
